tags: Doctor friendliness,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,Explanation of the health issue,
review:
I had an appointment for 11 AM. At 11.05 AM Doctor joined me at the dental chair. I had two issues. 
One, slight transient pain at the tip of front upper tooth. Doctor examined it and explained the reaon of the pain as being due to sensation of chewing which was tranmitting to the nerve due to micro-capillaries. Doctor ensured which tooth was involved and applied desensitization drug. Doctor advised to use tooth paste like sensodyne to alleviate this problem.
Two, filling of two cavities in the lower teeth. Doctor filled the cavities superbly using his expertise.
Total time taken was one hour.
reply_text: Thank you sir for the detailed insight üôè
